'''賈斯汀·詹姆斯·威爾森'''（{{lang-en|Justin James Wilson}}，{{bd|1987年|8月18日}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的投手，目前效力於辛辛那提紅人。生涯曾效力過海盜、洋基、老虎、小熊、大都會與洋基等隊。他曾於2008年拿下大學世界大賽的冠軍。

==職業生涯==
===匹茲堡海盜===
[[2008年美國職棒大聯盟選秀|2008年美國職棒大聯盟選秀]]，海盜隊在第5輪選進了威爾森。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=FB&p_theme=fb&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=12127F73124EA928&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM |title=Bulldogs double up in baseball's draft |accessdate=September 4, 2013 |archive-date=2014-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141113160849/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=FB&p_theme=fb&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=12127F73124EA928&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM |dead-url=no }}</ref>2012年8月20日，威爾森登上大聯盟。<ref>{{cite web|title=Pirates recall McPherson, Wilson|last=Janes|first=Chelsea|date=August 20, 2012|url=http://pittsburgh.pirates.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20120820&content_id=37033236&notebook_id=37037628&vkey=notebook_pit&c_id=pit|work=MLB.com|accessdate=November 13, 2014|archive-date=2013-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131102010747/http://pittsburgh.pirates.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20120820&content_id=37033236&notebook_id=37037628&vkey=notebook_pit&c_id=pit|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在初登板主投一局無失分，並送出3次三振。

2013年，他拿下6勝1敗，防禦率2.08。2014年，他拿下3勝4敗，防禦率4.20。<ref>{{cite news | url=https://nypost.com/2014/11/12/yankees-trade-francisco-cervelli-to-pirates-for-lefty-reliever/ | work=New York Post | first=Joel | last=Sherman | title=Yankees trade Francisco Cervelli to Pirates for lefty reliever | date=November 13, 2014 | accessdate=2020-05-25 | archive-date=2019-09-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190924230435/https://nypost.com/2014/11/12/yankees-trade-francisco-cervelli-to-pirates-for-lefty-reliever/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>

===紐約洋基===
2014年11月12日，海盜隊用威爾森向洋基隊交易[[弗朗西斯科·瑟維里|弗朗西斯科·瑟維里]]。<ref>{{cite news|title=Pirates acquire Cervelli from Yankees for Wilson|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/wire?section=mlb&id=11867724|agency=Associated Press|publisher=ESPN.com|date=November 13, 2014|accessdate=November 13, 2014|archive-date=2014-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141113163534/http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/wire?section=mlb&id=11867724|dead-url=no}}</ref>而洋基隊也讓威爾森擔任[[佈局投手|佈局投手]]，並讓[[戴林·貝坦西斯|戴林·貝坦西斯]]和[[安德魯·米勒_(棒球員)|安德魯·米勒]]在8、9兩局登板，組成這年洋基隊的牛棚勝利方程式。而威爾森在這年拿下5勝0敗，防禦率3.10。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nj.com/yankees/index.ssf/2015/12/yankees_to_trade_reliever_justin_wilson_2_reports.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-05-25 |archive-date=2017-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170423033555/http://www.nj.com/yankees/index.ssf/2015/12/yankees_to_trade_reliever_justin_wilson_2_reports.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===底特律老虎===
2015年12月9日，洋基將威爾森交易至老虎，換來[[查德·格林|查德·格林]]和Luis Cessa。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.tigers.mlb.com/news/article/159266762/yankees-trade-justin-wilson-for-prospects|title=Yankees land pair of pitching prospects for Wilson|first=Bryan|last=Hoch|work=MLB.com|date=December 9, 2015|accessdate=December 9, 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304101015/http://m.tigers.mlb.com/news/article/159266762/yankees-trade-justin-wilson-for-prospects|dead-url=no}}</ref>隔年1月13日，威爾森與老虎隊簽下1年152萬5000美元的合約以避免薪資仲裁。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.tigers.mlb.com/news/article/161848998/tigers-agree-to-terms-with-justin-wilson|title=Tigers avoid arbitration with Wilson|first=Jason|last=Beck|publisher=MLB.com|date=January 13, 2016|accessdate=January 13, 2016|archive-date=2016-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161008155719/http://m.tigers.mlb.com/news/article/161848998/tigers-agree-to-terms-with-justin-wilson/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在老虎隊的第一年投出4勝5敗，防禦率4.14的成績。

2017年1月13日，他與老虎隊簽下1年270萬美元的合約。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://m.tigers.mlb.com/news/article/213442814/tigers-avoid-arbitration-with-six-players/|title=Tigers maintain streak, agree to deals with six|publisher=MLB.com|first=Jason|last=Beck|date=January 13, 2017|accessdate=January 13, 2017|archive-date=2017-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170115162823/http://m.tigers.mlb.com/news/article/213442814/tigers-avoid-arbitration-with-six-players/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在這年球季的前11場出賽都沒有被敲出任何安打和失分，直到4月29日才被[[梅基·卡布瑞拉|梅基·卡布瑞拉]]敲出全壘打。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cbssports.com/mlb/gametracker/recap/MLB_20170429_CHW@DET/ |title=Cabrera, Abreu, Chisox beat Tigers 6-4 in 10, 6th win in row |publisher=CBSsports.com |date=April 29, 2017 |accessdate=April 30, 2017 |archive-date=2017-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170430065045/http://www.cbssports.com/mlb/gametracker/recap/MLB_20170429_CHW@DET |dead-url=no }}</ref>5月9日，由於原終結者[[法蘭西斯科·羅德里奎茲|法蘭西斯科·羅德里奎茲]]表現不佳，因此威爾森成為球隊新任終結者。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://bleacherreport.com/articles/2708788-francisco-rodriguez-replaced-as-tigers-closer-by-justin-wilson |title=Francisco Rodriguez Replaced as Tigers Closer by Justin Wilson |publisher=bleacherreport.com |date=May 9, 2017 |accessdate=May 18, 2017 |archive-date=2020-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200815024353/https://bleacherreport.com/articles/2708788-francisco-rodriguez-replaced-as-tigers-closer-by-justin-wilson |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===芝加哥小熊===
2017年7月31日，老虎隊將[[艾力克斯·艾維拉|艾力克斯·艾維拉]]和威爾森交易至小熊，換來Jeimer Candelario、Isaac Paredes與一名日後指定球員。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.freep.com/story/sports/mlb/tigers/2017/07/31/detroit-tigers-trade-justin-wilson-alex-avila-chicago-cubs-prospects/524411001/ |title=Deal done: Tigers trade Justin Wilson, Alex Avila to Cubs for prospects |newspaper=Detroit Free Press |first=Anthony |last=Fenech |date=July 31, 2017 |accessdate=July 31, 2017 |archive-date=2021-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210502192000/https://www.freep.com/story/sports/mlb/tigers/2017/07/31/detroit-tigers-trade-justin-wilson-alex-avila-chicago-cubs-prospects/524411001/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://m.tigers.mlb.com/news/article/245479820/tigers-trade-justin-wilson-alex-avila-to-cubs/|title=Tigers acquire prospect Candelario from Cubs|first=Jason|last=Beck|publisher=MLB.com|date=July 31, 2017|accessdate=July 31, 2017|archive-date=2017-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170803021524/http://m.tigers.mlb.com/news/article/245479820/tigers-trade-justin-wilson-alex-avila-to-cubs/|dead-url=no}}</ref>威爾森在小熊投得很掙扎，他出賽23場比賽，17.2局的投球就送出19次的保送，防禦率高達5.09。總計他2017年共拿下4勝4敗，防禦率3.41，並拿下13次救援成功。

2018年1月12日，威爾森與小熊簽下1年425萬美元的合約。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/cubs/news/kris-bryant-sets-record-for-first-year-raise/c-264617048|title=Kris Bryant sets record for first-year raise|website=MLB.com|language=en|access-date=2018-01-17|archive-date=2019-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129235858/https://www.mlb.com/cubs/news/kris-bryant-sets-record-for-first-year-raise/c-264617048|dead-url=no}}</ref>而他在球季結束後成為自由球員。

===紐約大都會===
2019年1月28日，威爾森與大都會隊簽下2年1000萬美元的合約。<ref>{{cite web|last1=DiComo|first1=Anthony|title=Mets officially sign Wilson, designate Cecchini|url=https://www.mlb.com/mets/news/justin-wilson-officially-signs-with-mets/c-303260422|website=MLB.com|publisher=[[MLB|MLB]]|date=January 28, 2019|accessdate=January 29, 2019|archive-date=2019-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129235919/https://www.mlb.com/mets/news/justin-wilson-officially-signs-with-mets/c-303260422|dead-url=no}}</ref>該年他的防禦率為2.54。隔年他出賽23場比賽，防禦率3.66。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/player/justin-wilson-458677?stats=career-r-pitching-mlb&year=2021|title = Justin Wilson Stats, Fantasy & News}}</ref>

===重返洋基===
2021年2月23日，威爾森和洋基簽下1年合約。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/justin-wilson-yankees-deal|title=Yanks add to 'pen in reunion with LHP Wilson}}</ref>該年他在洋基拿下1勝1敗，防禦率7.50。

===辛辛那提紅人===
2021年7月28日，洋基將威爾森和Luis Cessa交易到紅人，換來一名日後指定球員。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/31902010/new-york-yankees-trade-relievers-luis-cessa-justin-wilson-cincinnati-reds|title=Yankees trade relievers Cessa, Wilson to Reds|date=July 28, 2021|website=ESPN.com}}</ref>

==投球風格==
威爾森的主要球種有均速95-96英里的二縫線與四縫線快速球(最快球速可達99英里)，還有均速90-94英里的切球。另外他還會搭配均速約83-87英里的曲球做變化。<ref>{{citeweb |url=http://www.fangraphs.com/pitchfx.aspx?playerid=4301&position=P |title=Justin Wilson PitchFX at FanGraphs.com |publisher=fangraphs.com |accessdate=June 7, 2014 |archive-date=2017-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170924080612/http://www.fangraphs.com/pitchfx.aspx?playerid=4301&position=P |dead-url=no }}</ref>

